 Whinsley Masara, Chronicle Reporter A POLICE officer stationed at Binga Police Station has been arrested for allegedly sneaking into a house and raping a vendor while she slept. Constable Onismo Kabone (42), under the Minerals and Border Control Unit, allegedly raped a 33-year-old woman (name withheld for ethical reasons) of Garikai Compound in Binga. More to follow. . .